<item>
            <title>[LU-12252] sanity-hsm test 220A, 220a, 221, 223b, 224A, 224a, 226 fail with &#8216;The expected changelog was not emitted&#8217;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12252</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-hsm test_220A, 220a, 221, 223b, 224A, 224a, 226 fail with &#8216;The expected changelog was not emitted&#8217;. We see this for PPC client testing only.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at the client 1 (vm1) dmesg log for a recent failure,  &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/82a14510-668f-11e9-8bb1-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/82a14510-668f-11e9-8bb1-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;, we see an &#8216;invalid record&#8217; message for most of these failures&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[ 2678.768679] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == sanity-hsm test 220A: Changelog for archive ======================================================= 06:01:49 (1555999309)
[ 2681.992599] Lustre: 31712:0:(llog_cat.c:783:llog_cat_process_common()) lustre-MDT0000-mdc-c000000076f9e800: invalid record in catalog [0x5:0x0:0xa]:0: rc = -22
[ 2681.992753] LustreError: 31712:0:(mdc_changelog.c:236:chlg_load()) lustre-MDT0000-mdc-c000000076f9e800: fail to process llog: rc = -22
[ 2682.153063] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  sanity-hsm test_220A: @@@@@@ FAIL: The expected changelog was not emitted 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are no other errors seen in the dmesg and copytool logs. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Logs for other failures are at&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/0352f31e-6322-11e9-8bb1-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/0352f31e-6322-11e9-8bb1-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c3ef7fae-5f6f-11e9-9646-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c3ef7fae-5f6f-11e9-9646-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
